msgid ""
"In Ekos :doc:`Focus <ekos-focus>`, :doc:`Guide <ekos-guide>`, "
"and :doc:`Align <ekos-align>` modules, captured images are displayed in the "
"embedded FITS Viewer. The embedded viewer includes a *floating bar* that can "
"be used to perform several functions:"
msgstr ""

